snippet.textDisplay: Okay, but I feel like you were being way too dramatic about this. 😹 it’s basically like a more savory chicken and waffles? But with a different “meat” protein. I think it you would’ve shredded down the hotdogs more, cooked them before you added the egg in, and looked up a proper vegan beer cheese, this would’ve killed. Cheese and hotdog is great. The egg in the recipe isn’t supposed to be really thought of as egg but more of a binding agent. This recipe is fine, it just needs spruced up. 😹
